    <sys:String x:Key="Manager_ProtectedChip">Protected by Windows</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Manager_ProtectedTooltip">Windows won’t let this component be removed.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Manager_EdgeNote">Microsoft blocks Edge removal on recent Windows versions. WinMate will close Edge, unlock the uninstaller, and run it. If your copy of Windows enforces the block, Edge might stay put.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Explain_Tooltip">Explain what this does and whether it’s worth turning on</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Explain_Close">Got it</sys:String>
